creator: Easy Utility
descriptionHtml:
Send bulk message without add whatsapp numbers in contacts

You can send message to whatsapp contacts manually send entered mobile number

How to use?

Step 1) Enter bulk mobile numbers or Upload bulk numbers via excel sheet(You can download demo file from excel tab).

Step 2) After entering bulk mobile numbers you can check all number for valid or not, so you can remove duplicate mobile numbers.

Step 3) Now enter Message whatever you like.

Step 4) Enter interval time for sending messages between two numbers(Default interval time is 10 seconds only).

Step 5) If you have image for promotion you can Select/Capture image.

Step 6) At last step if Accessibility Service is not enabled then by clicking "Send Message" button you will redirect to accessibility service setting after that you can send bulk message.

Notes :

By using business account please send message up to maximum limit of 500 mobile numbers because your business account may suspend.

By using personal account please send message up to maximum limit of 100 mobile numbers because your personal account may suspend.
